                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 1v: He who donated this book to (the church of) the Savior of the World (in) Çähat is Bahta Gäbrä Kidan (together with) Wälättä Täklä Haymanot, with his daughter Wälättä Täklä Haymanot and his son(s) Gäbrä Mikaʾel (and) Mǝḥrätä Wäld (and) his wife Ḫirutä Śǝllase Täklä Haymanot.</q>
                           The first part of the note (up to ጨሃት፡) is written in red ink. The number 10 may be an attempt to write a wrong letter, later cancelled.
Crude notes are added below, apparently on the same subject.
                        </item>
